This is a phased digital marketplace that connects project-sellers (start: municipalities) with capital providers (banks, funds, HNIs, retail). Phase-1 is a simple commitment-based flow for municipal projects; later phases add loan pools, bidding, tranches, and tokenisation. The platform’s success depends on strict admin validation, high-quality documents (DataRoom), clear access controls, and a robust audit/notification system. 

