Core business flow (simple)

Seller (municipality) creates a Listing with project details + uploads DPRs to a DataRoom. 

BA_Field_Catalogue

Admin validates listing & documents; once validated listing goes Live. 

Marketplace_Vision

Buyers view DataRoom → place Commitments/Bids (Phase-1 commit_amount; Phase-2 add price/yield). 

BA_Field_Catalogue

Platform runs allocation/auction logic → Allocation recorded. Settlement happens off-platform (proof uploaded). 

Marketplace_Vision

Ongoing: Q&A, project updates, notifications, audit trail.

