BA_Field_Catalogue

POST /api/listings/{id}/commitments — place commitment/bid. 

BA_Field_Catalogue

POST /api/listings/{id}/admin/validate — admin validation action. 

BA_Field_Catalogue

GET /api/listings/{id}/dataroom?granted=true — show documents user can see. 

