Final insight (one sentence)

This BRD is solid — it focuses on a low-friction Phase-1 (municipal projects) to prove marketplace value while keeping the data model future-ready for lending pools, tranches and tokenisation; your main priorities: data/document quality, admin validation, clear access controls, and an auditable settlement proof flow.